    General Stores in Borivali, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. Any of these stores house a vast variety of products ranging from loose grains and pulses to cosmetics. The vast list of general store items does not limit to food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. Mentioned above is a vast list of General Stores in Borivali, Mumbai.
